### 🧠 My Favorite Projects

- 🔬 [**Image Dehazing & Accurate Image Segmentation using Advanced Deep Learning**](https://github.com/shanmugaraj-d/Image-Dehazing-and-Accurate-Image-Segmentation-using-Advanced-Deep-Learning-Techniques)  
  → Improved image clarity by ~7dB PSNR and boosted segmentation accuracy to 92%.

- 📉 [**Attrition Analysis in IT Organizations**](https://github.com/shanmugaraj-d/Attrition-analysis-and-reporting-in-an-IT-organization)  
  → Uncovered employee turnover insights with real business implications.

- 🎬 [**Sentiment Analysis of Netflix Reviews**](https://github.com/shanmugaraj-d/Netflix-Review-Sentiment-Analysis)  
  → Compared traditional TF-IDF + LR vs. RoBERTa-based classification, hitting 87% accuracy.

